node.text:
With its jaw-dropping limestone formations and an ancient temple tucked into the stunning landscape, Wulong Karst is a perfect blend of natural beauty and rich cultural heritage.

#china #chongqing #wulongkarst #photography #voyaged #earth #chinadestinations #madewithlightroom #earth
@little_stephy0925 thank you bro 😍 was a great mood there that morning
What a gem!!! Great one bro☺️👍
@maximmosk haha das stimmt! 😃 vielen dank maxim! war wirklich sehr eindrücklich dort, spezieller ort 😍
Eine der seltenen Landschaftsaufnahmen bei dir 😉 Sieht mega eindrücklich aus diese Schlucht 😍
@jasmineyang1116 such a nice place, did you like it too?
@throughlucaslens Haha yes! I posted it before
I was there several years ago! 😂
It's even more magical with the clouds 😍👏
@quetzalcoatlst haha thank you so much bro 😍 did you watched the movie?
Insane shot! Optimus prime might show up though 😂
What a nice escape from the city
@mike.visionz thank you bro 😍 I was lucky with the mood that day
What a sick location and you captured it beautifully 🤌🏽🔥
